sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as Bruger
    participant iOS as iOS App
    participant AppState as AppState
    participant Bridge as WatchAppSyncBridge
    participant WC as WatchConnectivity
    participant WatchBridge as watchOS WatchAuthSyncBridge
    participant WatchStore as WatchWorkoutStore
    participant Supabase as Supabase anon + RLS

    User->>iOS: Logger ind / ændrer profiltilstand / completion state
    iOS->>AppState: Opdaterer session, settings og profile_mode
    AppState->>Bridge: Bygger WatchAuthSyncPayload
    Bridge->>WC: updateApplicationContext(payload)
    Bridge-->>WC: fallback transferUserInfo(payload)
    WC->>WatchBridge: Leverer payload til watchOS
    WatchBridge->>WatchBridge: Validerer schemaVersion og gemmer lokalt
    WatchBridge->>WatchStore: Payload til repository bootstrap
    WatchStore->>Supabase: Restore session med user token + anon key
    Supabase-->>WatchStore: RLS-scoped workout, trackerlog og cycle data
    WatchStore-->>User: Dagens træning og log/afslut flow på watch

